  "about_the_game": "Protocol Five is a story-driven surreal horror adventure. Trapped in a distorted world following a mysterious experiment, you must find your way to freedom with the help of your colleague. You are an expert who knows Protocol 5 very well and you know that it can solve the problem, but you also know that it should never be used.<br><br>Gameplay:<br>The game is heavily focused on narrative, alternating dialogues with simple challenges and puzzles. In the second part of the game, you will receive a gun and face more action-packed survival horror sections. Some dialogues will allow you to make philosophical choices that will irremediably change the course of the story, leading you to one of 5 possible endings.<br><br>Duration:<br>The main path can be completed in 2-4 hours, each alternate path has unique gameplay elements not present in the other paths and is complementary to the narrative and overall experience.<br><br>Theme:<br>The game explores themes of philosophical choices regarding eternity, using a minimalist style. The difficulty is not high, aiming to offer a surreal experience through dialogues.<br><br>Performance:<br>Developed by one person with Unreal Engine, it targets 60fps at 1080p at the high-quality setting, with options to reduce quality and increase fps on older hardware.<br><br><br>You will find yourself in a distorted world, populated by disgusting creatures who want to kill you..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935290/extras/7d78ece5ecb564dff41a06c0664698cb.poster.avif?t=1755370734\" width=400 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935290/extras/7d78ece5ecb564dff41a06c0664698cb.webm?t=1755370734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2935290/extras/7d78ece5ecb564dff41a0